      "description": "SyncIndexesError constructor parameters don't match the interface - takes SchemaType param but should match MongoDB error pattern"
    },
    {
      "file": "types/expressions.d.ts", 
      "line": 133,
      "description": "Round expression accepts optional second parameter with incorrect syntax 'NumberExpression?' - should be 'NumberExpression | undefined'"
    },
    {
      "file": "types/expressions.d.ts",
